<list id="fs-idp81216" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha"><item>are more likely to develop asthma</item>
<item>tend to have less perceived control</item>
<item>are more likely to develop cardiovascular disorders</item>
<item>tend to tolerate stress well</item>
</list></problem>
