<problem id="fs-idp146288">
<para id="fs-idm182352">The concept of learned helplessness was formulated by Seligman to explain the ________.</para>
<list id="fs-idm106192" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha"><item>inability of dogs to attempt to escape avoidable shocks after having received inescapable shocks</item>
<item>failure of dogs to learn to from prior mistakes</item>
